Prophet Paseka ‘Mboro’ Motsoeneng was among those who supported prophet Shepherd Bushiri at the Pretoria Magistrates Court on Monday. Addressing Bushiri supporters outside the court, Mboro told them he was there to support their prophet emotionally. "Our relationship stared last year, this is the reason why I’m here, he said to loud cheers. Bushiri and his wife were arrested on Friday for alleged fraud, money laundering and contravention of the Prevention of Organised Crime Act. 